videos.headline: Darnold fumble recovered by Utah
videos.description: Dradlee Anae recovers the ball after a Sam Darnold fumble.

videos.headline: Singleton takes screen 53 yards
videos.description: Raelon Singleton catches the screen pass and cuts up field for a big gain for Utah.

videos.headline: Smith intercepts Williams
videos.description: Cameron Smith jumps to intercept Troy Williams, ending the Utes' drive in the red zone.

videos.headline: Darnold fumble results in Utah TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold's second fumble of the game is recovered by Marquis Blair and returned for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Darnold hits Petite for 52-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold responds to two fumbles by throwing a touchdown pass to Tyler Petite.

videos.headline: Wilson catches tipped ball for big pick up
videos.description: Siaosi Wilson reels in a tipped pass and turns up field for a 40-yard gain.

videos.headline: Moss rumbles and stumbles for 31-yard run
videos.description: Zach Moss gives a Marshawn Lynch-type effort on 31-yard first down run.

videos.headline: Williams catches TD on trick play touchdown
videos.description: Quarterback Troy Williams catches a pass from Demari Simpkins for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Williams hits Simpkins for TD
videos.description: Demari Simpkins catches a 32-yard touchdown pass from Troy Williams.

videos.headline: Thompson makes catch by his fingertips
videos.description: Bryan Thompson uses every inch of his hands to reel in a 29-yard pass from Troy Williams.

videos.headline: Vaughns 1-handed catch picks up 1st down
videos.description: Sam Darnold escapes the pass rush and hits Tyler Vaughns who makes a one-handed catch to pick up the first down.

videos.headline: Darnold hits Petite for another TD
videos.description: Sam Darnold throws his second touchdown pass of the game to Tyler Petite.

videos.headline: Darnold ties it with TD to Falo
videos.description: Sam Darnold rolls out and connects with Josh Falo on a one-yard touchdown pass to tie it 21-21.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Darnold ties it with TD to Falo) 2017/10/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: USC's Jones II flips into end zone for TD and lead
videos.description: USC RB Ronald Jones II gets hit and flips in mid-air into the end zone for the go-ahead touchdown against Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USC's Jones II flips into end zone for TD and lead) 2017/10/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah converts on 4th down
videos.description: Troy Williams passes to Siale Fakailoatonga on fourth down to pick up the first down and then some.

videos.headline: Williams 1-yard TD
videos.description: Troy Williams runs for a touchdown late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Utah fails go-ahead 2-pt conversion attempt
videos.description: Utah falls to USC after Troy Williams' run comes up short on the two-point conversion attempt.

videos.headline: Darnold taking dramatic win in stride
videos.description: Sam Darnold talks with Todd McShay after USC's 28-27 victory over Utah.
